Participated in @developer_dao x @MinaProtocol Hackathon this week and the results are out 🥁🥁🥁
🏆 Won third place overall for zkTalents and among the three blog post winners.
Here's what we made ⬇️

Developer DAO (🧱, 🚀): 🚨  @minaprotocol x D_D    🚨 
🚨 HACKATHON WINNERS 🚨 
This hackathon was a great success wrapping up with 30 submissions after 8 days of hacking!  There were so many great submissions, but we've narrowed it all down to:
3 Overal Winners
3 Blog Winners
3 Starter Kit Winners
